Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:19.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:30.17,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.94,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:42.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:48.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:58.06,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:06.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:12.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:24.17,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:43.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Having been made the target of the Zentradi forces\Nand been effectively banished from the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross continues to wander\Nour solar system aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:54.34,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Max, who met Milia thanks to a video game\Ngot her to agree to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,He is off to meet her with a heart filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:09.55,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(73,151)}VIRGIN ROAD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:18.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is late. I wonder if she'll show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I ask her to meet me in a park\Nat night? Maybe she got spooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should have suggested somewhere\Nmore conventional, like a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilian Jenius!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:42.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia! I just got here myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:54.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Zentradi soldier, Queadluun-Rau\NFlight Commander Milia Fallyna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentradi soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the knife! This is a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel? With me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the knife! This is revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's revenge, I guess I don't\Nhave much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:11.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, revenge? For who? Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother? Your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:21.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten? This is for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:26.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Zentradi, I have enjoyed the\Nreputation of being the deadliest of pilots,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and I cannot forgive this humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not once but twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,you have forced me to know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the shame of defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I despise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost for a third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,K... Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So adorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have the top brass said anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can really get formal asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:22.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're can't, then we'll...\Nwe'll end up as refugees in outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Cheer up, okay? Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:38.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I request your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Max, why so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, it concerns marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:52.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just barely had your first\Ndate with her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping straight into marriage is pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We're both certain that\Nwe want to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Only, it puts her in an awkward position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:04.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is awfully fast.\NIs it her parents or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that. It's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:13.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be a Zentradi pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an enemy soldier?! Her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! No way!\NYou two can't get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your language, your customs and your ways\Nof thinking are all different!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:28.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our love is strong enough to conquer all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:33.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is for idiots! It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can count on that for anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When two hearts come together as one,\Neven the impossible becomes possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In theory, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:46.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But in real life, love soon gets\Nshattered to pieces, like glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you speaking from\Nexperience, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'd like you to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You brought her with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:57.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is ladylike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:20.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this could be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:26.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, you should formally present\Nthis to Captain Global.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You're marrying an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Wait, isn't that Milia Fallyna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ace pilot of the Lap'Lamiz Fleet\Nis getting "married"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Married"? What is "married"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I gather, it entails men\Nand women living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:59.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're saying that men and women\Npair off and live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:05.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Men and women living together...\NIf that's their custom, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:11.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are they accepting Milia,\Nwho is both an alien and an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They should kill her,\N yet they are celebrating this "married." Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:20.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:25.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. It is an emotion that\Nis indispensable to their society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, eh? The concept is unimaginable to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:34.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One could posit that the soldiers who\Ndeserted fell under love's spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to seek asylum with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:40.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't understand\Nhow they felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:59.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand in hand, this has been the\Nnewlyweds' first task as a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, let's have a few words from\Nthe sponsor of this wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:07.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore Global, captain of the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore Global!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, Milia, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The marriage of these two is a\Npairing of great significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, Milia was a pilot\Nfor the Zentradi forces;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:29.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,someone whom, for we of the Macross,\Nmerely hating would not be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, we continue to come\Nunder attack by the Zentradi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and are unable to return to the Earth, our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:43.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be only natural for the people aboard\Nthis ship to utterly despise the Zentradi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:45.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However! I repeat, however!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It does us no good to hate each and\Nevery one of their soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:56.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, from the moment they were born,\Nthey have known nothing but war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:01.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, they say that they\Nwish to stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to live in peace, they have defected from the Zentradi forces
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and come to the Macross seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, we were uncertain.\NShould we even let them on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We worked to find a common\Nground between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:23.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, we have learned that they\Nare human, with the same blood as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:30.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have also learned that they simply want to\Nlive with us here on the Macross as brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:35.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Macross, as part of\NUN Forces, hereby announce
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:39.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the formal acceptance of the\NZentradi soldiers seeking asylum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Captain for ya! Whatta fine man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:54.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be difficult for those of us who\Nhave lost loved ones in the conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:12:00.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but our duty now is to cast those feelings\Naside and come together as...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:04.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What can Global be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to understand that, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can save the Earth now is\Ncompassion, like the Captain has shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:17.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, please call off the\NGrand Cannon operation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly do that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:23.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, we humans fought long and\Nbloody wars amongst ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Language, the color of our skin,\Nideology, religion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We overcame these and other obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and have finally brought the beginnings\Nof peace to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:38.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to do this. Why can't\Nwe help the Zentradi do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:42.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Peace in space." Is this not our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:45.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By giving this marriage our full support,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:49.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be taking the historic\Nfirst step toward that goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.68,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Captain Hayase,\Nour dream is finally coming true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The miclones have lived in hiding\Nand on the fringes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:38.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,yet they have inflicted serious damage upon us,\Nand created a situation even more grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:44.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any further disorder within the Zentradi\Nforces would be extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:51.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we must eliminate the miclone homeworld\Nas well as the root of this unrest: the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack them with all the ships in the main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:22.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max and Milia, a very special someone has\Nrushed here in order to celebrate your marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our very own idol, the\Nsuperstar of the century:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, Milia, congratulations on your marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:53.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And to all our friends who have\Ncome here from the Zentradi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,let's work hard to build a\Nwonderful future together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:01.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'd like to sing about the happiness\Nthat comes from the union of our two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:09.63,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,As you prepare to set\Nout on your journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:16.07,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, you silently\Nrouge your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:22.82,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,From behind your white veil,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:30.08,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,You await that one, shining moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:36.08,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,As fondness becomes love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:41.36,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,And love becomes tenderness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:51.53,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Engraved in the heart of the\None dearest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:16:01.73,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the two will be\Nforever in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:10.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, with love, the differences between\Nworlds don't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Britai Kridanik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have orders from Lord Bodolzaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet will commence an all-out\Nassault on the Macross at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:25.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate the Macross and everyone aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.55,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,...silently rouge your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Britai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's finally come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:36.44,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,From behind your white veil
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We must launch an all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't attack the Macross...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:58.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It's an order! We can't disobey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. Let's get ready for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:17.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? An attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get to your stations immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:31.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, you don't have to fight.\NJust stay with your bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll fight! All right, Milia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:42.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that a wife stands by her husband\Nand helps him, so that's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Zentradi, I, too,\Nam known as an ace pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:49.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if we die a glorious death\Nin battle on our wedding day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:53.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:02.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they have picked some\Nother day to attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:06.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing them isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hit them there,\Nyou'll just disable them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I don't want to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But WE could be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die by your side, then I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Crack the shell, but let what's inside live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia, just watch me work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, please overlook\Nthe way I'm fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Overlook it?! Max...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! Let me give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked! This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Blocks D-3 and D-7 have taken damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighth battle pod unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:30.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you scrambled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are looking at me\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,W... What? What\Nare you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We want a cease-fire with the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the order to halt the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Negotiations for a cease-fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:02.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Britai, soldiers are mutinying\Nthroughout the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:06.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Some soldiers have raised arms against their\Ncommanding officers when ordered to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Britai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, cease fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:23.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that goes against the\NSupreme Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Pull everyone back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:30.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the men that our fleet will enter into\Ncease-fire negotiations with the miclones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:31.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C... Captain! The enemy\Nfleet is withdrawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:47.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be thanks to that wedding broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quick! Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:15.30,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, have some consideration,\Nwould you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you to put oil in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You said to take the water in\Nthis kettle and heat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:30.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bottle, and it's got oil in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is called a bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's the kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. It's gonna take some work\Nbefore I can get a cup of coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:47.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:35.06,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(84,108)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:35.06,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,458)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:42.00,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Exsedol has come aboard the Macross\Nas the first official envoy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,since the war with the Zentradi began.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:47.62,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease-fire negotiations are underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:53.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is merely the prelude\Nto a terrifying destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:57.45,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.51,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"MESSENGER"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:24:01.46,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(73,139)}MESSENGER
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:22.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:29.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.91,0:24:35.76,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.45,0:24:43.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.39,0:24:50.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:56.67,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.85,0:25:04.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.41,0:25:15.80,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
